    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill based gameplay!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Are you quick enough to slide underneath the sizzling slime balls, catch the game-winning airstrike, and nuke the last brick cluster into oblivion? Or should you play it safe and use a calculated bank shot to trigger that dynamite chain in a flurry of combo hits? It’s all about combining movement, timing and precision with split-second decision making.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/41c903f8aef0ff2f9cb2a025d6ec7404.poster.avif?t=1730229874\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/41c903f8aef0ff2f9cb2a025d6ec7404.webm?t=1730229874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/41c903f8aef0ff2f9cb2a025d6ec7404.mp4?t=1730229874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progressive levels filled with challenges!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smash your way through 50 levels carefully designed to gradually challenge even the most seasoned veterans of the genre. It seems easy at first, but one wrong move and you'll find yourself back at the checkpoint, wishing you hadn't hit that floating  laser switch with your combo split!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/3eca69ba6cea4a2e5886aca16a63a6e7.poster.avif?t=1730229874\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/3eca69ba6cea4a2e5886aca16a63a6e7.webm?t=1730229874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/3eca69ba6cea4a2e5886aca16a63a6e7.mp4?t=1730229874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Devious enemies, interactive obstacles and detailed power-ups!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against shifting bricks, death beams, explosive barrels, hover mines, floating portal fiends, fireballs, and laser traps. You'll have your paddle shrunk, slimed, and even insta-killed by death itself. You'll drop airstrikes, load up blasters, toggle trap doors, crack safes, raise shield walls, toggle lasers, maybe even bounce a bomb into a cluster of bunker bricks for some sweet, sweet revenge!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/173b77b003f2124b1d82f583af73feb4.poster.avif?t=1730229874\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/173b77b003f2124b1d82f583af73feb4.webm?t=1730229874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3158980/extras/173b77b003f2124b1d82f583af73feb4.mp4?t=1730229874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No Bomb-Bats or Slimegoons were harmed in the making of this game*</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*We did lose a few Skulls when a Spikey fractured.</p>",
